      543.9,
      258.35
    ],
    "text": "Board on contract basis, and their contracts had gone on till December,",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      99.02,
      265.47,
      543.89,
      279.47
    ],
    "text": "2015. The Sri Lanka Transport Board in October 2015 has taken a",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      99.02,
      286.59,
      543.94,
      300.59
    ],
    "text": "decision to absorb the 06 Petitioners to the permanent cadre. This is",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      99.02,
      307.71,
      543.79,
      321.71
    ],
    "text": "reflected in 2R5. But this decision has not been implemented and after",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      99.02,
      328.83,
      547.55,
      342.83
    ],
    "text": "December 2015 the contracts of the Petitioners had not been extended.",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      99.02,
      349.95,
      543.81,
      363.95
    ],
    "text": "The Petitioners therefore complained that their fundamental rights",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      99.02,
      371.07,
      547.67,
      385.07
    ],
